metadata.name: Evening walk
metadata.description:
The shot captures the undisturbed backwaters in my hometown- Kumbalam, a small island in the suburbs of Kochi.

Kochi, being the Queen of Arabian sea, capturing the pulse everyday in the backwater had been an amazing journey for me.
